data.description: Welcome to this delightful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home built in 2010. Spanning 1,651 sqft, this residence features an open living area with vaulted ceiling, seamlessly connecting to the dining area and kitchen. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry, great size pantry and a convenient pass-through window, making entertaining a breeze. Laundry area off the kitchen, washer and dryer are included for added convenience. Retreat to the primary bedroom for peaceful relaxation, while three additional bedrooms offer versatility for various needs.Step outside to a covered back patio, ideal for enjoying outdoor moments in any weather. The landscaped yard is perfect for relaxation or gardening. Two car garage with wireless access, fantastic curb appeal, and new roof and gutters installed summer 2023. Conveniently located near China Spring HWY, making it an easy commute to all things in town. This home combines modern comforts with convenience, offering a perfect opportunity for a fulfilling lifestyle. [ Walk through the home here from your couch: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=WTyXj5Wo6EU&mls=1 ]
